<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Self-Referral Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-size: 14px;

    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .content {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .content a {
      color: #1a73e8;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .footer img {
      max-width: 100px;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    table,
    th,
    td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    th,
    td {
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    th {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Email if ‘Yes’ to any question – Review needed -->
     <div class="email-container">

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello&nbsp;{{RecipientName}},</p>

      <p>
        Your answers from the Provide Physiotherapy Self-referral platform
        below, related to your significant back injury, shows you require a
        review.
      </p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Question</th>
            <th>Answer</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {{#each questions}}
          <tr>
            <td>{{question}}</td>
            <td>{{answer}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>
        We advise you to contact NHS 111 if your back injury happened in the
        last 6 weeks or book an appointment with a First Contact
        Physiotherapist (FCP), a service now provided by most GP practices
        throughout your local area.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please contact your GP surgery to see if you have access to this
        service and if not, please book an appointment with your GP.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please provide this information to the healthcare professional
        reviewing you.
      </p>

      <p>Kind regards,</p>
      <p>
        <strong>Smart Referral System</strong>&nbsp;|&nbsp;Provide Online
        Referral Service
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <img src="logo.png" alt="Smart Referral System Logo" />
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>